dia=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/GettyImages-1305625722-6370e64.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=90&amp;resize=406%2C271, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/GettyImages-1305625722-6370e64.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=814%2C543 2x\" type=\"image/webp\"><source media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/GettyImages-1305625722-6370e64.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=406%2C271, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/GettyImages-1305625722-6370e64.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=814%2C543 2x\" type=\"image/jpeg\"><source media=\"(min-width: 590px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/GettyImages-1305625722-6370e64.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=90&amp;resize=555%2C370\" type=\"image/webp\"><source media=\"(min-width: 590px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/GettyImages-1305625722-6370e64.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=555%2C370\" type=\"image/jpeg\"><img class=\"wp-image-622142 align size-landscape_thumbnail image-handler__image image-handler__image--aspect no-wrap js-lazyload\" data-src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/GettyImages-1305625722-6370e64.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=619%2C413\" width=\"620\" height=\"413\" alt=\"Michal Kwiatkowski wearing Kask Wasabi helmet at Strade Bianche\" title=\"Michal Kwiatkowski wearing Kask Wasabi helmet at Strade Bianche\"></source></source></source></source></source></source></source></source></source></source></source></source></source></source></picture></div><div class=\"caption-hold\"><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span class=\"caption-copy\"><i class=\"icon-arrow icon-camera-circle\"></i> Michal Kwiatkowski was among the Ineos Grenadiers riders to wear the new helmet at Strade Bianche.</span></figcaption><span class=\"im-image-caption\"> <i>Tim de Waele / Getty Images</i></span></div>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ventilation is adjusted by sliding up and down the middle panel in the shell, opening or closing vents. </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">It’s a similar feature to the <a href=\"https://www.bikeradar.com/news/lazers-second-iteration-of-the-bullet-aero-helmet-is-here/\">Lazer Bullet 2.0 helmet</a>, which also has a central sliding vent that moves up to let air flow through a wide vent at the front of the helmet and via internal channelling to the large vents at the rear. </span></p>\n<div class=\"image-handler__container image-handler__container--full\" style=\"padding-bottom: calc(100% * (1077 / 1617));\">\n    <picture><source media=\"(max-width: 320px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/3_KASK_Wasabi_opened_closed-88228e5.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=90&amp;resize=300%2C200, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/3_KASK_Wasabi_opened_closed-88228e5.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=600%2C400 2x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/3_KASK_Wasabi_opened_closed-88228e5.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=900%2C599 3x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/3_KASK_Wasabi_opened_closed-88228e5.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=1200%2C799 4x\" type=\"image/webp\"><source media=\"(max-width: 320px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/3_KASK_Wasabi_opened_closed-88228e5.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=300%2C200, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/3_KASK_Wasabi_opened_closed-88228e5.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=600%2C400 2x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/3_KASK_Wasabi_opened_closed-88228e5.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=900%2C599 3x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites