_Merino_wool_design-00e139c.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=1239%2C826 2x\" type=\"image/webp\"><source media=\"(min-width: 992px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/Wasabi_Merino_wool_design-00e139c.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=620%2C413, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/Wasabi_Merino_wool_design-00e139c.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=1239%2C826 2x\" type=\"image/jpeg\"><source media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/Wasabi_Merino_wool_design-00e139c.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=90&amp;resize=407%2C271, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/Wasabi_Merino_wool_design-00e139c.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=815%2C543 2x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/Wasabi_Merino_wool_design-00e139c.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=1223%2C815 3x\" type=\"image/webp\"><source media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/Wasabi_Merino_wool_design-00e139c.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=407%2C271, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/Wasabi_Merino_wool_design-00e139c.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=815%2C543 2x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/Wasabi_Merino_wool_design-00e139c.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=1223%2C815 3x\" type=\"image/jpeg\"><source media=\"(min-width: 590px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/Wasabi_Merino_wool_design-00e139c.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=90&amp;resize=555%2C370, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/Wasabi_Merino_wool_design-00e139c.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=1110%2C740 2x\" type=\"image/webp\"><source media=\"(min-width: 590px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/Wasabi_Merino_wool_design-00e139c.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=555%2C370, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/Wasabi_Merino_wool_design-00e139c.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=1110%2C740 2x\" type=\"image/jpeg\"><img class=\"wp-image-622123 align size-landscape_thumbnail image-handler__image image-handler__image--aspect no-wrap js-lazyload\" data-src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/Wasabi_Merino_wool_design-00e139c.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=620%2C413\" width=\"620\" height=\"413\" alt=\"Kask Wasabi\" title=\"Kask Wasabi\"></source></source></source></source></source></source></source></source></source></source></source></source></source></source></picture></div><div class=\"caption-hold\"><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span class=\"caption-copy\"><i class=\"icon-arrow icon-camera-circle\"></i> The pads on the inside of the helmet are made of Merino wool.</span></figcaption><span class=\"im-image-caption\"> <i>Kask</i></span></div>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">The Wasabi is designed to be aero too. Even with the vent open, Kask says there’s only one watt extra drag compared to it being closed. </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">It claims that its wind tunnel testing shows that the Wasabi is second only to the <a href=\"https://www.bikeradar.com/news/team-sky-and-kask-launch-new-aero-helmet-at-tour-down-under/\">Kask Utopia</a> in slipperiness among the high-end helmets it tested. </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Elsewhere, Kask uses its Octo Fit retention system in the Wasabi, which is also found in its other helmets. And Kask says that despite its fancy venting, a size medium Wasabi weighs only 290g. </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Kask has yet to announce colour options and pricing, but we do know that it will be available in sizes small, medium and large.</span></p>","author":"Paul Norman","siteTitle":"BikeRadar","siteHash":"df99dd1320fcd97327a2def4c67247c08cd4090a7dab684a0eddb9b856f80ef1","entryHash":"5e0f2b0e770dd01419f0194e84efba76f3e181863bf3b4c81f6969c4066c9f6d","category":"Cycling"}